thread.title: Asian Stocks Struggle Though China Growth Supports

author: Ese Erheriene
title: Asian Stocks Struggle Though China Growth Supports
text:
Asian tech under pressure following ZTE action Sterling around post-Brexit high Earnings from Goldman Sachs, IBM eyed European stocks and S&P 500 futures climbed Tuesday, even as U.S. and U.K. warnings over a Chinese telecommunications-equipment giant put pressure on Asian markets.
The Stoxx Europe 600 inched up 0.2% in the early minutes of trading after solid earnings reports helped stocks inch higher on Wall Street Monday in the lowest volume day so far this year.
